item.title: Don't Use Or Ingest Ginger If You Have Any of These Four Conditions
item.description: Ginger is a highly nutritious plant. In fact, it’s widely used as a folk medicine for a number of conditions. That’s because its active components, including gingerol and shogaols, have a ton of health benefits to offer.
